# Chesster local / Vercel environment variables.
#
# Copy this file to `.env.local` (for `vercel dev`) or paste individual
# values into the Vercel dashboard for production. None of these are
# strictly required — the app degrades gracefully:
#
#   • Without LLM vars:       coach uses template fallbacks.
#   • Without Supabase vars:  sync + accounts turn off, local IndexedDB
#                             remains the source of truth.
#
# DO NOT commit `.env.local`. `.gitignore` already excludes it.

# --------------------------------------------------------------------
# LLM (Phase 7)
# --------------------------------------------------------------------

# Force the LLM proxy off regardless of other settings. Useful for
# private/internal deploys that never want to talk to Anthropic.
# DISABLE_LLM_PROXY=1

# Reserved for the deferred "free-tier" shared-quota mode (DESIGN.md
# §12a). Leave BOTH unset for BYOK-only v1. Setting only one of them
# keeps the server in `byok-only` mode.
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-api03-...
# FREE_TIER_DAILY_CAP_CENTS=0

# --------------------------------------------------------------------
# Supabase (Phase 9 — not required for Phase 8 BYOK launch)
# --------------------------------------------------------------------

# Client-side (baked into the Vite build).
# VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
# VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=eyJ...

# Server-side (serverless functions only).
# SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=eyJ...

# --------------------------------------------------------------------
# Observability (optional)
# --------------------------------------------------------------------

# VITE_SENTRY_DSN=
# SENTRY_DSN=
